estimate DY|X(y|x), its marginal continuous variates [X|X>0, Y > 0] and [Y|X>0, Y > 0] undergo normal quantile transformation (NQT), yielding

standard normal variates U = Œ¶‚àí1[DX(x)] and V = Œ¶‚àí1[DY(y)]. Following the meta-Gaussian distribution theorem of Kelly and Krzysztofow-

