ùë•}]2ùëëùë•

(A5)

where Fi denotes the CDF of PQPF at the ith forecast instance and yiis the verifying observation. I (.) is the indicator (step) function which takes the value of 1 if x ‚â• yi and 0 elsewhere. Continuous ranked probability skill score (CRPSS) is routinely used to assess the performance of
probabilistic forecast relative to a reference forecast

